    {
      "id": "633182bbc871b5002382fa79",
      "text": "骸晶",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1664189117,
      "updated": 1664189117
    },
    {
      "id": "633182bce600350000a56db2",
      "text": "骸晶(がいしょう)",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1664189117,
      "updated": 1664189118
    },
    {
      "id": "633182bde600350000a56db3",
      "text": ">[結晶]の隅および稜の部分のみが急速に成長して，結晶面の中央部の成長が遅れたために面が形成されず，その結果凹んだ不完全な面に囲まれた結晶の形状をいう．不完全な結晶の形で特定の方向のみに成長するか，または平行連晶の集まった形となるもので，枝分れした中空の形や[燕尾服]のような形を示すことがある［Rosenbusch : 1887, Hatch : 1888］．",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1664189118,
      "updated": 1664189118
    },
    {
      "id": "633182bde600350000a56db4",
      "text": "[https://kotobank.jp/word/%E9%AA%B8%E6%99%B6-781931 骸晶とは - コトバンク]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1664189118,
      "updated": 1664189118
    },
    {
      "id": "633182bde600350000a56db5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1664189118,
      "updated": 1664189118
    },
    {
      "id": "633182bde600350000a56db6",
      "text": "英語では[Hopper crystal]という",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1664189118,
      "updated": 1664189118
    },
    {
      "id": "633182bde600350000a56db7",
      "text": "　画像のような[ビスマス]結晶が有名",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1664189118,
      "updated": 1664189118
    },
    {
      "id": "633182bde600350000a56db8",
      "text": "　　ビスマス以外にも[方鉛鉱]、[石英]([水晶])、[金]、[方解石]、[岩塩]、[氷]なども骸晶になり得る",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1664189118,
      "updated": 1664189118
    },
    {
      "id": "633182bde600350000a56db9",
      "text": "　ビスマスの骸晶はネット通販でも買える",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1664189118,
      "updated": 1664189118
    },
    {
      "id": "633182bde600350000a56dba",
      "text": "　[https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/30/Bismuth_crystal.jpg]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1664189118,
      "updated": 1664189118
    },
    {
      "id": "633182bde600350000a56dbb",
      "text": "　[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hopper_crystal Hopper crystal - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1664189118,
      "updated": 1664189118
    },
    {
      "id": "633182bde600350000a56dbc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1664189118,
      "updated": 1664189118
    },
    {
      "id": "633182bde600350000a56dbd",
      "text": "[https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/ef/Bismuth_crystals_and_1cm3_cube.jpg][https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/75/Bi-crystal.jpg]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1664189118,
      "updated": 1664189118
    },
    {
      "id": "633182bde600350000a56dbe",
      "text": "[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%83%93%E3%82%B9%E3%83%9E%E3%82%B9 ビスマス - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1664189118,
      "updated": 1664189118
    },
    {
      "id": "633182bde600350000a56dbf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1664189118,
      "updated": 1664189118
    },
    {
      "id": "633182bde600350000a56dc0",
      "text": "ビスマスは通販でも購入でき、極端に高価なものでもないため骸晶作りの動画は無数にある",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1664189118,
      "updated": 1664189118
    },
    {
      "id": "633182bde600350000a56dc1",
      "text": "　[https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=ビスマス%E3%80%80結晶 「ビスマス　結晶」でYoutube検索]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1664189118,
      "updated": 1664189118
    },
    {
      "id": "633182bde600350000a56dc2",
